<section id="imagen_index">
	<h1>About Us</h1>
</section>
<div class="container_conocenos">
	<div class="hero-conocenos">
		<div class="texto-principal">
			<p>
				<strong>We are a company committed to sustainability and
					the environment.</strong> We have created a platform that connects volunteers
				with events, allowing them to participate and collaborate to
				make each event a more ecologic, more responsible, and socially conscious
				experience.
			</p>
			<p>Our goal is to promote volunteering in the event managing area,
				encouraging teamwork, respect for the environment, and social awareness in
				every activity.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- Section: Our History -->
	<div class="seccion-historia">
		<h2>Our story</h2>
		<p>
			Voluntariado Verde was born in <strong>2025</strong> thanks to a
			group of athletes and environmental activists who shared the same
			mission: To transform sports events into engines of positive change
			for our planet. What began as a small local initiative in <em>Bilbao</em>
			has now become a network of over <strong>5,000</strong> active
			volunteers across <em>Spain</em>.
		</p>
		<p>
			Every year we collaborate in more than <strong>200</strong>
			events, from marathons and triathlons to surfing and mountain biking
			competitions, ensuring that each event leaves a positive mark on the
			environment and local communities.
		</p>
	</div>

	<!-- Section: Mission, Vision, and Values -->
	<div class="tarjetas-mision">
		<div class="tarjeta tarjeta-mision">
			<h3>Our Mission</h3>
			<p>Make the connection between committed volunteers and
				event organizers easier, promoting sustainable actions that
				minimize environmental impact and maximize social benefit.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="tarjeta tarjeta-vision">
			<h3>Our Vision</h3>
			<p>To be a European benchmark in organizing sustainable
				volunteering, inspiring millions of people to combine their passion
				for sports or music with caring for the planet.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="tarjeta tarjeta-valores">
			<h3>Our Values</h3>
			<p>Environmental commitment, teamwork, social inclusion,
				transparency, continuous innovation, and respect for all people and
				communities we collaborate with.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- Section: Why Join Us -->
	<div class="seccion-unirse">
		<h2>Why join Voluntariado Verde?</h2>
		<ul class="lista-beneficios">
			<li><strong>Unique experience:</strong> Experience different types of events
				from the inside, with privileged access and unforgettable moments.</li>
			<li><strong>Continuous training:</strong> We offer free courses
				on sustainability, first aid, and event management.</li>
			<li><strong>Active community:</strong> Be part of a network of
				people committed to the environment.</li>
			<li><strong>Certifications:</strong> Obtain recognized volunteer
				certificates that improve your CV.</li>
			<li><strong>Real impact:</strong> Every action counts.
				Contribute directly to making sports a more sustainable activity.</li>
		</ul>
	</div>

</div>
